    "title": ".ok Package Install Reliability",
    "summary": "Fixes 'not a gzip file' when installing ZIP-format .ok packages built by Okama Studio. Adds archive magic validation after store download and clearer diagnostic messages.",
    "notes": [
      "Fix: _is_zip() now detects all ZIP magic signatures and falls back to zipfile.is_zipfile() for edge-case archives.",
      "Fix: _sniff_content() diagnostic helper reports whether a file is HTML, JSON, empty, or unknown instead of cryptic gzip errors.",
      "Fix: download_game() validates archive magic bytes after download to catch 404 pages served as HTML.",
